    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Bis-HPMA Poly(Dimethylcyclohexane/Hexane Carbonate)/IPDI Copolymer is a urethane polymer formed by a multi-step process. First, a polyester is made by condensing Dimethylolcyclohexane, Hexanediol, and Dimethyl Carbonate, which is subsequently reacted with Isophorone Diisocyanate. The resulting polymer is end-capped with Hydroxypropyl Methacrylate"
